<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Verify Email Address</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        p {
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p>Hi,</p>
        <p>You have requested to verify your email address</p>
        <p>The OTP to verify your email address is <strong>{{verificationCode}}</strong>.</p>
        <p>Please ignore this message if you did not initiate this request.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>